original_title:
New The Texas Redistricting Map is here.

It eliminates 5 Democrats Seats:
🔵 9th Green.
🔵 28th Cuellar.
🔵 29th Garcia.
🔵 32nd Johnson.
🔵 34th Gonzalez.

The districts are now Republican:
🔴 9th R+15.2 .
🔴 28th R+10.4 .
🔴 29th R+17.7 .
🔴 32nd R+10.1 .
🔴 34th R+10.3 .  — The Donald
article_summary: Texas Redistricting Map has been released, eliminating 5 Democratic seats and making them Republican, shifting the balance to 30R-8D. The change has sparked debate on the potential impact on Hispanic voters and the possibility of creating more Republican districts.</s>
